  "session": "2026RS",
  "identifier": "HB 195",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to the Kentucky Urban Youth Agriculture Initiative.",
  "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 247 to define terms; establish the Kentucky Urban Youth Agriculture Initiative to promote farming to youth in urban counties with a pilot program in at least 1 University of Kentucky Cooperative Extension Service office by September 1, 2026; set each program term to 1 year in duration, beginning each January; establish guidelines and participant eligibility.",
